Here is the cleaned up text:

Service Intelligence Setup

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS

* To manage Data Cloud: Data Cloud Admin permission set
* To manage Service Cloud: Service Cloud User permission set
* To install Service Intelligence: Service Intelligence App Admin permission set
* To use Service Intelligence: Service Intelligence User permission set

NOTE Data Cloud must be enabled and setup in order to start these steps.

Create a Data Cloud Salesforce CRM Connection
Enable Service Cloud Features
Update the Data Cloud Salesforce Connector Permission Set
Install the Service Data Kit for Service Intelligence
Enable CRM Analytics for Service Intelligence
Install Service Intelligence
Monitor, Update, and Delete Service Intelligence Apps
Delete Service Intelligence Apps
title: Service Intelligence Setup and Installation
